{"tid":1199771,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［請統一野餐時間］1100 11/6定係0500 12/6","createTime":"2019-06-10T14:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T15:47:00.000Z","uid":160619,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"87212cf950752f7d65b907ab669103038608be1f","tid":1199771,"uid":160619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:47:07.000Z","msg":"［好重要，請廣傳］<br />\n<br />\n十一點到要捱十二個鐘 同要考慮會唔會有唔夠人嘅情況出現 消耗有生力量 但如果齊人夠人 有得諗<br />\n<br />\n十二點到交通極唔方便 到達時間太散 部分人會黎唔到 物資組唔方便 但可以保存體力 前提係你之前真係可以充分休息<br />\n<br />\n記得預時間搭車同交通擠塞嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n一定要有共識，否則等同賣甩早到嘅人<br />\n<br />\n十一號十一點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十二號五點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b0af9cd2af886bc33ce7b4976e2a65ef8149bb","tid":1199771,"uid":160619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:47:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc732afaabad3ce690e97eaff5e39981508f76c3","tid":1199771,"uid":160619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:47:37.000Z","msg":"臨時改時間其實都不利"},{"pid":"4a0b3ac631d6d5b0bbc8a346d0c6a50ad998d309","tid":1199771,"uid":8290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8855fc9940b0d38fdd77012eeac896c05bdf9635","tid":1199771,"uid":160619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:48:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31dbd243465480608afa66a22b95dc90eec6bc8a","tid":1199771,"uid":160619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:49:18.000Z","msg":"可以講吓原因"},{"pid":"87d0c36d923057cc3ebdab9139d6c60175f6dea5","tid":1199771,"uid":160619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:51:17.000Z","msg":"唔該推一推"},{"pid":"ce3dd358eb6c61d08efc21eafaf349ace3ff56a5","tid":1199771,"uid":160619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:5